\"false\" data-ms-editor=\"true\"> ​​Specializujeme se na výrobu kuchyní na míru\ns&nbsp;využitím moderních technologií a výrobních nástrojů. Vaši kuchyň\ns vámi naplánujeme aby nejen vypadala hezky, ale byla také praktická a\nfunkční pro každodenní používání.</p>\n                      <a href=\"[[site_path_live]]/kuchyne/\" class=\"u-align-left u-border-active-black u-border-hover-black u-border-radius-50 u-btn u-button-style u-hover-feature u-hover-white u-border-2 u-border-white u-black u-block-3641-26\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" data-current-state=\"default\" data-hover-preset-name=\"border\" data-css=\"{&quot;default&quot;:{&quot;color&quot;:&quot;black&quot;,&quot;border&quot;:2,&quot;border-color&quot;:&quot;white&quot;,&quot;transform&quot;:&quot;translateX(0) translateY(0) scale(1) rotate(0deg)&quot;,&quot;gradient&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;borders&quot;:&quot;top right bottom left&quot;},&quot;hover-on-group&quot;:{&quot;border&quot;:2,&quot;border-color&quot;:&quot;grey-75&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;shadow&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:&quot;0px&quot;,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;0px&quot;,&quot;blur&quot;:&quot;0px&quot;,&quot;spread&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;black&quot;,&quot;transparency&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;toString&quot;:null,&quot;toJSON&quot;:null},&quot;border-radius&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;transform&quot;:&quot;scale(1) translateY(px)&quot;,&quot;text-color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;text-shadow&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:&quot;0px&quot;,&quot;y&quot;:&quot;0px&quot;,&quot;blur&quot;:&quot;0px&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;black&quot;,&quot;transparency&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;toString&quot;:null,&quot;toJSON&quot;:null,&quot;spread&quot;:null}}}\">kuchyně</a>\n                      \n                    <editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\"><style>\n  @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style><div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div></editor-squiggler><editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\"><style>\n  @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style><div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div></editor-squiggler></div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"u-size-30 u-size-60-md\">\n                <div class=\"u-layout-col\">\n                  <div class=\"u-align-center u-container-align-left u-container-style u-layout-cell u-palette-2-base u-right-cell u-size-20 u-block-3641-27\" data-hover-preset-name=\"slideIn\" data-animation-name=\"customAnimationIn\" data-animation-duration=\"2000\">\n                    <div class=\"u-container-layout u-valign-middle u-block-3641-28\">\n                      <h3 class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-default u-block-3641-29\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-ms-editor=\"true\">Výroba nábytku</h3>\n                      <p class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-default u-block-3641-30\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-ms-editor=\"true\"> ​Zabýváme se výrobou nábytku na míru, jako jsou\nvestavěné skříně, koupelnový nábytek, vybavení dětských pokojů a kancelářských\nprostor. Při výrobě používáme pouze kvalitní a ověřené materiály.&nbsp;<br>\n<!--[endif]--></p>\n                      <a href=\"[[site_path_live]]/vyroba-nabytku/\" class=\"u-align-left u-border-active-white u-border-hover-white u-border-radius-50 u-btn u-button-style u-hover-feature u-hover-white u-border-2 u-border-white u-palette-2-base u-block-3641-31\" data-animation-name=\"customAnimationIn\" data-animation-duration=\"1500\" data-animation-delay=\"250\" spellcheck=\"false\" data-ms-editor=\"true\" data-current-state=\"defa