e u-layout-cell u-size-30 u-image-1\" data-image-width=\"866\" data-image-height=\"1155\" data-animation-name=\"customAnimationIn\" data-animation-duration=\"2000\" data-animation-delay=\"250\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;[[site_path_live]]/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_1717.jpeg&quot;);\">\n                  <div class=\"u-container-layout u-container-layout-1\"></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"u-container-align-left u-container-style u-layout-cell u-size-30 u-white u-layout-cell-2\">\n                  <div class=\"u-container-layout u-container-layout-2\">\n                    <h3 class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-3\"> Vnitřní okenní plastové\nparapety</h3>\n                    <p class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-4\"> Okenní plastové parapety jsou určeny pro všechny\ntypy interiérů.&nbsp;<br><!--[endif]-->\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-5\">\n                      <span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Př</span><b>ednosti plastových parapetů:</b>\n                      <br><!--[endif]-->\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-6\">\n                      <li> vynikající stálost barev\njednotlivých dekorů</li>\n                      <li>v<span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">ysoká pevnost a tuhost nosného\nmateriálu</span>\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li>\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">mechanická odolnost vrchního laminátu</span>\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li>\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">dlouhá životnost</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li style=\"\">\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">malá tepelná roztažnost</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li style=\"\">\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">příznivá cena</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li style=\"\">\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; background-color: #ffffff; color: #111111; font-family: Montserrat,sans-serif;\">velký výběr dezénů</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n                      <style> @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style>\n                      <div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div>\n                    </editor-squiggler>\n                    <editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n                      <style> @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style>\n                      <div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div>\n                    </editor-squiggler>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"u-size-30\" style=\"\">\n              <div class=\"u-layout-row\" style=\"\">\n                <div class=\"u-container-align-left u-container-style u-layout-cell u-palette-2-base u-size-30 u-layout-cell-3\">\n                  <div class=\"u-container-layout u-container-layout-3\">\n                    <h3 class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-7\"> Vnitřní okenní\ndřevotřískové parapety</h3>\n                    <p class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-8\"> Povrch dřevotřískového parapetu tvoří vysoce\noděruvzdorný laminát CPL/HPL, který se používá běžně na pracovní desky a je\ndodáván předními výrobci laminátu v Evropě.&nbsp;</p>\n                    <editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n                      <style> @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style>\n                      <div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div>\n                    </editor-squiggler>\n                    <p class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-9\"> P<b>řednosti dřevotřískových\nparapetů</b>\n                    </p>\n                    <ul class=\"u-align-left u-text u-text-10\">\n                      <li>snadná údržba a montáž&nbsp;</li>\n                      <li>stálobarevnost a odolnost proti\nUV záření&nbsp;</li>\n                      <li style=\"\">dlouhá životnost&nbsp;</li>\n                      <li>estetika a luxusní vzhled</li>\n                      <li>všestranné použití</li>\n                      <li>zdravotně nezávadné&nbsp;</li>\n                      <li>velký výběr dezénů</li>\n                      <li>příznivá cena</li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n                      <style> @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style>\n                      <div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div>\n                    </editor-squiggler>\n                    <editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n                      <style> @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style>\n                      <div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div>\n                    </editor-squiggler>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"u-container-align-center u-container-style u-image u-layout-cell u-size-30 u-image-2\" data-image-width=\"866\" data-image-height=\"1155\" data-animation-name=\"customAnimationIn\" data-animation-duration=\"2000\" data-animation-delay=\"500\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;[[site_path_live]]/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/IMG_1776.jpeg&quot;);\">\n                  <div class=\"u-container-layout u-container-layout-4\"></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <editor-squiggler style=\"height: 0px; width: 0px;\">\n        <style> @media print {\n    .ms-editor-squiggler {\n        display:none !important;\n    }\n  }\n  .ms-editor-squiggler {\n    all: initial;\n    display: block !important;\n    height: 0px !important;\n    width: 0px !important;\n  }</style>\n        <div class=\"ms-editor-squiggler\"></div>\n      </editor-squiggler>\n    </section>\n    \n    \n    \n  \n'),(1878,423,'_np_html','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><head>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"​A Leade